objenome.goal

Class DoubleFitness

  • java.lang.Object
    • objenome.goal.DoubleFitness
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Fitness>, Fitness
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleFitness.Maximise, DoubleFitness.Minimize

    public abstract class DoubleFitness
extends java.lang.Object
implements Fitness
    Represents a Fitness score as a double value. The natural ordering of a fitness represented as a double may be either maximising or minimising. A maximising fitness considers an individual with a larger fitness score as being fitter than one with a smaller score. With a minimising fitness the opposite is true. Fitness scores may range from Double.MIN_VALUE to Double.MAX_VALUE.
